      "article_id": "48c7037bf51d4b92c7fbdc952dec9c84",
      "title": "Delta Air Lines Airbus A330-300 Returns To Amsterdam Due To Landing Gear Retraction Issues",
      "link": "https://simpleflying.com/delta-air-lines-airbus-a330-300-amsterdam-landing-gear-retraction/",
