      "title": "NETA NATTER | BJP LEADER SUFFERS GAFFE AT PUBLIC EVENT",
      "link": "https://www.deccanchronicle.com/360-degree/neta-natter-bjp-leader-suffers-gaffe-at-public-event-1828330",
