      "article_id": "19919c96463390a668ed942d5a58f63d",
      "title": "DR Congo launches mpox vaccination drive amid global alarm, rising death toll",
      "link": "https://www.firstpost.com/world/dr-congo-launches-mpox-vaccination-drive-amid-global-alarm-rising-death-toll-13822470.html",
