      "article_id": "751fd9a0b47c7c9aabea06d4525e2d03",
      "title": "Israel uses regional conflicts as excuses for occupation: Turkish President Erdogan",
      "link": "https://www.aa.com.tr/en/middle-east/israel-uses-regional-conflicts-as-excuses-for-occupation-turkish-president-erdogan/3352531",
      "keywords": null,
