      "article_id": "bcb44bd348270810a5f959f9956d1672",
      "title": "70 killed in gang attack in violence-plagued Haiti",
      "link": "https://www.manilatimes.net/2024/10/06/world/americas-emea/70-killed-in-gang-attack-in-violence-plagued-haiti/1979718",
