      "article_id": "0513df29d9f587dc5df79c1033ef8b99",
      "title": "Biden 'not confident' of peaceful US election",
      "link": "https://www.manilatimes.net/2024/10/06/world/americas-emea/biden-not-confident-of-peaceful-us-election/1979716",
